 ff6 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;imme-</div><div class="t me4b xe h4a y2014 ff6 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">diately </div><div class="t m241a x28 h4 y175f ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">after the tribulation.&quot; Mark says, &quot;after that tribula-</div><div class="t m843 x4 h4 y6b7 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">tion.&quot; The &quot;tribulation&quot; here mentioned is no doubt that</div><div class="t m49 xa9 h4 y6b7 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">. </div><div class="t m15a xa9 h4 y6b7 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"> long </div><div class="t m13a1 x4 h4 y18bc ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">period of- &quot;time and times and the dividing of times,&quot; or &quot; forty </div><div class="t ma88 x4 h4 y411 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and two months&quot;— 1260 days, or years — in which the papal </div><div class="t m15a1 x4 h4 yba9 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">power was to make war on the saints and blaspheme God. See </div><div class="t m7c3 xe h4 y1788 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Dan. 7:25 and Rev. 13:5. This period ended in 1798. By means </div><div class="t m6af x4 h4 y16db ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of the. Reformation the persecution ended before the period ,itself </div><div class="t m71e x4 h4 y20b2 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">expired. Immediately following the close of the persecution the </div><div class="t m8c2 x4 h4 y1f31 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">sun was to be darkened. </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
